1
00:00:24,810 --> 00:00:25,655
Come in.

2
00:00:29,990 --> 00:00:33,993
You called me,  Is something wrong?

3
00:00:35,852 --> 00:00:36,867
Sit down first, dear.

4
00:00:44,230 --> 00:00:45,833
I want to talk to you for a moment...

5
00:00:45,883 --> 00:00:49,076
about the shareholders' and investors' party this Saturday.

6
00:00:49,980 --> 00:00:50,818
Why?

7
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:58,732
It’s going to be the day we finally destroy Pimchat completely.

8
00:01:02,775 --> 00:01:06,486
Now... don’t look at me with those eyes.

9
00:01:08,390 --> 00:01:10,061
What exactly are you planning to do, mom?

10
00:01:20,730 --> 00:01:21,630
Sign this.

11
00:01:22,350 --> 00:01:26,584
It’s the contract agreeing to your engagement with Mr. Kimhant.

12
00:01:33,450 --> 00:01:34,055
No!

13
00:01:35,270 --> 00:01:36,215
I won’t sign it.

14
00:01:38,960 --> 00:01:40,461
You have to sign it!

15
00:01:41,390 --> 00:01:43,261
I already told you I’d do it, Mom!

16
00:01:43,286 --> 00:01:45,335
What more do you want from me?

17
00:01:45,540 --> 00:01:48,190
And how can I be sure you’ll keep your word?

18
00:01:48,770 --> 00:01:51,526
Or are you planning to betray me? Huh?

19
00:01:57,270 --> 00:01:58,633
Do this for me, Ran.

20
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:02,590
And do it for your Pimchat, too.

21
00:02:04,970 --> 00:02:08,184
It’s better to let her step down gracefully from her position

22
00:02:09,490 --> 00:02:11,249
than to have the whole country accusing her

23
00:02:11,810 --> 00:02:14,258
of having an affair with her own sister.

24
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:15,243
Mom!

25
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,489
Now, sign it.

26
00:02:39,544 --> 00:02:40,843
Is this what you wanted?

27
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:43,495
Mom!

28
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,873
Yeah

29
00:03:35,570 --> 00:03:37,464
My apologies for startling you, Khun Ranya.

30
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:41,323
It’s fine.

31
00:03:43,850 --> 00:03:45,347
But please... don’t ever do something like this again.

32
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:51,704
In a little while, your mom is going to announce our engagement.

33
00:03:52,510 --> 00:03:54,104
Why are you still acting so guarded?

34
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:57,784
Hey…

35
00:03:58,683 --> 00:04:00,953
Why keep playing hard to get?

36
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,381
Hello, Mr. Kimhan.

37
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:13,809
Oh, Ms. Chat!

38
00:04:14,650 --> 00:04:16,196
I haven’t seen you for a long time.

39
00:04:17,050 --> 00:04:18,553
I thought you hadn't returned to Thailand yet.

40
00:04:19,932 --> 00:04:21,930
Actually, I’ve been back for a while now.

41
00:04:21,969 --> 00:04:23,458
It’s just that things have been so busy at the company,

42
00:04:23,470 --> 00:04:24,990
so I haven't really been out to many events.

43
00:04:27,270 --> 00:04:30,326
You haven't changed at all.

44
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:40,160
And you haven't changed either, Mr. Kimhant.

45
00:04:41,950 --> 00:04:44,209
Uh, Mr.Kim,

46
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:47,920
My mom has something she'd like to discuss with you.

47
00:04:48,812 --> 00:04:49,489
Yes sir.

48
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:25,932
Everyone, thank you all so much

49
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:28,738
for joining us tonight.

50
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:34,560
I am delighted to announce to you all

51
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:37,747
that what Mr. Wichai left unfinished,

52
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:42,375
I and my daughter, Ranya,

53
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:45,335
will make it a reality

54
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:55,550
with the cooperation of our company and Mr. Kimhant’s Holder Group. 	

55
00:05:59,570 --> 00:06:01,360
Everyone, cheers!

56
00:06:06,740 --> 00:06:14,024
And I’d like to announce the happy news of Ranya and Mr. Kimhant’s engagement.

57
00:06:15,620 --> 00:06:17,969
Let’s have another toast to celebrate.

58
00:06:18,190 --> 00:06:18,947
Come on!

59
00:06:20,740 --> 00:06:22,880
That Kimhant is just a fool.

60
00:06:23,050 --> 00:06:26,775
A little bit of trickery and he fell right into the trap of obsessing over Ranya.

61
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,378
With a face that stupid,

62
00:06:29,409 --> 00:06:31,796
I’m going to make sure he loses everything!

63
00:06:31,827 --> 00:06:33,827
Hahaha!

64
00:06:33,858 --> 00:06:35,809
Turn it off right now! Turn it off!

65
00:06:37,126 --> 00:06:38,313
Turn it off!

66
00:06:38,540 --> 00:06:39,421
AI can be quite scary.

67
00:06:39,452 --> 00:06:40,233
Turn it off!

68
00:06:42,010 --> 00:06:44,276
Turn it off! Turn it off now!

69
00:06:45,290 --> 00:06:47,883
Ms. Jintana, what the hell is going on?

70
00:06:47,932 --> 00:06:49,692
Mr. Kimhant, please, just calm down first.

71
00:06:50,490 --> 00:06:51,858
That’s not my voice.

72
00:06:51,975 --> 00:06:53,236
I’m being framed!

73
00:06:53,267 --> 00:06:55,403
I... I never said anything like that.

74
00:06:55,433 --> 00:06:56,387
Please, just listen to me.

75
00:06:56,406 --> 00:06:57,255
If you didn't say it,

76
00:06:57,950 --> 00:06:59,126
then whose voice is it?

77
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:01,526
Mr. Kimhant, please stay calm.

78
00:07:01,544 --> 00:07:02,104
I’m being set..

79
00:07:02,129 --> 00:07:05,120
I don't care about the engagement anymore.

80
00:07:05,580 --> 00:07:07,907
And as for your projects.

81
00:07:08,140 --> 00:07:11,138
You can go ahead and manage them yourself.

82
00:07:11,163 --> 00:07:12,178
I’m out.

83
00:07:12,196 --> 00:07:13,821
Mr. Kimhant! Mr. Kimhant, wait...

84
00:07:13,846 --> 00:07:14,387
Mr. Kimhant, wait.

85
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:15,027
Jintana,

86
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:18,812
what about the money you asked us to invest earlier?

87
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:20,572
If it’s like this, our entire project is ruined!

88
00:07:20,683 --> 00:07:21,858
I can explain!

89
00:07:21,876 --> 00:07:23,138
That wasn't my voice at all!

90
00:07:23,150 --> 00:07:24,578
Everyone, please calm down.

91
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:33,827
I am Pimchat, the daughter of Khun Pimprapha, the founder of PS Group.

92
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:39,323
I sincerely apologize for what has happened.

93
00:07:40,670 --> 00:07:42,178
But please, don't worry.

94
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:46,147
I have a new project in the same location to present to you all.

95
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,627
For this project, we are going to build...

96
00:07:50,664 --> 00:07:52,135
Come here!

97
00:07:52,166 --> 00:07:52,701
Mom!

98
00:07:54,070 --> 00:07:55,827
Get over here! Right now!

99
00:07:56,290 --> 00:07:56,867
Mom.

100
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,800
This was your doing, wasn't it?! such a terrible daughter!

101
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,107
Mom, please... just stop.

102
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,526
Stop? Stop what?

103
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:08,689
Why should I stop?

104
00:08:09,090 --> 00:08:12,615
I did it for you!

105
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,618
I did it for you!

106
00:08:13,643 --> 00:08:15,150
I did it for you, for you, and for you!

107
00:08:15,175 --> 00:08:16,683
It was all for you!

108
00:08:16,713 --> 00:08:17,421
Mom.

109
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,707
I did it all for you.

110
00:08:18,732 --> 00:08:20,535
You only ever did it for yourself.

111
00:08:20,670 --> 00:08:22,578
You never actually did it for me.

112
00:08:26,130 --> 00:08:29,132
Mom... Mom, please just stop.

113
00:08:32,090 --> 00:08:33,544
Come and live with me.

114
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:37,046
Whatever you want, I’ll get it for you.

115
00:08:39,790 --> 00:08:41,667
But I want this company!

116
00:08:42,370 --> 00:08:44,806
So what? Can you get it for me? Huh?!

117
00:08:45,070 --> 00:08:46,369
Can you?!

118
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,138
You perverted freaks...

119
00:08:55,070 --> 00:08:55,870
you’re so obsessed with her

120
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:58,400
that you’d even hurt your own mother.

121
00:08:59,156 --> 00:09:00,147
Please, stop.

122
00:09:03,501 --> 00:09:04,030
Why?

123
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:06,627
You think you can stop me?

124
00:09:07,846 --> 00:09:09,840
Fine. If I’m going down.

125
00:09:10,210 --> 00:09:12,086
I’m taking you down with me!

126
00:09:14,393 --> 00:09:15,058
Mom.

127
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:24,732
It’s okay, Ran.

128
00:09:30,510 --> 00:09:32,824
I thought I could talk her around...

129
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:35,569
but I couldn't.

130
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,978
It’s okay, it’s okay. Don’t worry.

131
00:09:51,180 --> 00:09:53,563
Chat! We’re screwed.

132
00:09:53,710 --> 00:09:54,516
Look at this!

133
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,320
She really did you in.

134
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:01,009
What are we supposed to do now?
